0.4
===

Update README to explain the known "bug" caused by Gossip not correctly
dealing with an empty status.
When stopping playing, reset the status (since the user is no longer listening)
Save the original Gossip status, and use it when reseting the status.
Don't uselessly change the status when a song property is changed, but
it wouldn't affect the status.

